            <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">LTCM</ENAMEX> was secretive about how it made money, but the basic
idea went something like this. Imagine <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">two</NUMEX> assets--say, <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">Italian</ENAMEX> and German
