<ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">Italian</ENAMEX> stocks--and so on. In principle, at least, <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">LTCM</ENAMEX>'s computers--programmed
by those <ENAMEX TYPE="WORK_OF_ART">Nobel</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">laureates</ENAMEX>--allowed the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">firm</ENAMEX> to search for complex trading
